overview: In desperate need of help to conceive their first child, three couples (Lily Love, Donnie Rock, Adira Allure, Brad Newman, Paisley Porter, Seth Gamble) visit a top-rated Fertility Clinic. The couples soon discover the clinic employs some rather "unusual" techniques when the sexy Nurse (Skylar Snow) takes good care of the husbands while the horny Doctors (Charles Dera, Justin Magnum) plant their seeds into the wives...
title: The Fertility Clinic
